text: Velledopsis tanganycae is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1969. It is known from Tanzania.BioLib.cz - Velledopsis tanganycae. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Phrissomini Category:Beetles described in 1969
